-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers</change>\n\t\t<change when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography</change>\n\t    <change when=\"2020-12-17\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references</change>\n\t</listChange>\n        </revisionDesc>\n    </teiHeader>\n    <facsimile>\n        <surface type=\"front\">\n            <graphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000628_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana</desc>\n            </graphic>\n            <graphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000628.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana</desc>\n            </graphic>\n         </surface>\n    </facsimile>\n    <text>\n        <body>\n            <div type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\">\n                <ab>\n                    <lb n=\"1\"/>D(is) M(anibus) s(acrum)\n                    <lb n=\"2\"/>Abdalas Domi\n                    <lb n=\"3\" break=\"no\"/>tiae Domitiani\n                    <lb n=\"4\"/>magister magnus\n                    <lb n=\"5\"/>ovium qui bene vix(it)\n                    <lb n=\"6\"/>in officio ann(os) LXXX\n                </ab>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"apparatus\">\n                <p><!--external apparatus criticus (if applicable)--></p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#RW\">\n                <p>Sacred to the spirits of the dead; Abdalas, (slave of) Domitia (wife of) Domitian, great master of\n                    the sheep, who lived well in his job; eighty years old</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"commentary\">\n                <p><!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    <!--of Abdalas, head shepherd of Domitia Longina, wife of Domitian. Site is 15km east of Morgantina. Manganaro, ANRW 1988, p.17 attempts to contextualise, and praises Salmeri's discussion. Cf.IMusCat 120 for another slave of Domitia Longina, commemorated at Catania.--></p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"bibliography\">\n                <listBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    <bibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        <citedRange>1985.0483</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Wilson</author>\n                        <date>1990</date>\n                        <citedRange>215 n.102\n                            fig.175\n                        </citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/VF9MMBI9\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Salmeri</author>\n                        <date>1984</date>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/ME6MW6GJ\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001608\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001608</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Manganaro</author>\n                        <date>1988</date>\n                        <citedRange>17 n.62</c